We believe in the serendipity when people from diverse backgrounds come together to exchange ideas, build together and extend their networks.
				</p>
				<hr>
				<i class="_f25">
A group of startups from the four corners of Africa will travel across 4 cities in Europe to meet, exchange and network with other startups in Europe that venture in the same fields.
				</i>
